 Rs. 300 p.m as medical allowance to take care of OPD treatment.", "006-normal": "Govt. will perform identification of the illegible families for getting registered for the Health Scheme on the basis of socio-economic census (SECC) data 2011. Furthermore, the families/persons that have been left out in the census can be enrolled on the basis of a defined process.", "007-normal": "Source / Reference Link: https://www.republicworld.com/india-news/general-news/j-and-k-govt-announces-free-universal-health-coverage.html"}}